      public String toString()
      Returns a String representation of the following form:

      <userID>:<locationName>-<locationDescription>_(<longitude>,<latitude>)

      Underscore indicates a space. You must follow the spacing, etc. precisely.

      For example

      101:Stadium-Champions (75,65)
